asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Lib-Tech-Attack-Banana-EC2BTX-Snowboard-2013/270865P,default,pd.html  Attack the mountain with the Lib Tech Attack Banana EC2BTX Snowboard. This freestyle master features EC2 Eliptical Camber/Banana Blend. EC2 is C2 Technology enhanced, EC2 is Elliptical! We added Elliptical Camber, slightly shortened contact lengths and a smoother, more powder friendly tip and tail entry. The Elliptical camber moves the apex of the camber inward, which helps distribute tip and tail pressure more evenly, provides a more focused pop, and creates better suspension to absorb big landings. Excelling in all conditions, the Attack Banana can hit anything you have in sight and land effortlessly. Last year the Attack Banana won Transworld 2012 Good Wood award. The Attack Banana does not play defense it is truly an offensive machine that likes to beat up on mountains just for the fun of it.
